text: "Brass in Pocket" is the third single by The Pretenders. It is from their self-titled debut studio album. It went to number 1 in the United Kingdom, Ireland, South Africa and Sweden, number 2 in Australia and New Zealand and number 14 in the United States. ==References== Category:1979 songs Category:The Pretenders songs Category:Ultra Nat√© songs
